<h3>Weddings and receptions (up to 250 persons)</h3>

<p>Our expansive lawn and rolling hills offer a rustic backdrop for your wedding ceremony. Bride, groom, and attendants can use the classic farmhouse for wedding preparation, and an adjacent facility is perfect for serving refreshments and dinner to your guests.</p>

<p><strong>The ceremony</strong></p>
<p>When you book the Monarch, you have the property exclusively for the entire day. Only one event is permitted per day.</p>
<ul>
<li>The ceremony site on the lawn with a tree-filled backdrop</li>
<li>Bridal suite</li>
<li>Portable sound system</li>
<li>Chairs or benches</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>The reception</strong></p>
<p>The Monarch has an open policy on catering. You can hire the caterer of your choice. Your guests can mingle on the patio, lawn, and gardens.</p>
<ul>
<li>Reception facility or open air tent</li>
<li>Portable dance floor</li>
<li>Tables and chairs</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>The extras</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>You or your designer are responsible for decor</li>
<li>Paver patio</li>
<li>Landscape and patio lighting</li>
<li>Open Wi-Fi network</li>
<li>Background music for patio area</li>
<li>Convenient parking for guests</li>
<li>Potted plants and perennial gardens</li>
</ul>
<p></p>

